Spring JDBC
spring jdbc is a powerfull mechanism to connect to the database and execute Sql queries.

java program <-> spring jdbc module <-> database
                (JDBC template)

JDBC is API to perform operation and database.

problems of JDBC (old not spring jdbc)
1. we need to write a lot of code.
    - repeating all database code again and again.
2. exception handling problem : checked exception
    so you need to add try catch 

Spring JDBC overcome above problems

spring jdbc provide class jdbcTemplate which has all the important methods to perform operations with the database.

JdbcTemplate methods  ->
update() -> insert, update, delete....
execute -> select queries.....